```

git add .gitignore
git commit -m 'Add .gitignore'
git push origin add-gitignore

```

```
sed -i 's/Test change/For more info, check the wiki/' README.md # replace text
git add README.md
git commit -m 'Correct line in README.md'
git push origin update-readme
```
